date-released: "2026-03-08"
license: MIT
url: "https://github.com/adwantg/mcp-shield-pii"
repository-code: "https://github.com/adwantg/mcp-shield-pii"
abstract: >-
  Real-time PII redaction proxy for the Model Context Protocol (MCP).
  Intercepts MCP client-server communication to detect and mask 23 types
  of personally identifiable information using regex, NLP, and context-aware
  scoring — ensuring GDPR/HIPAA compliance before data reaches the LLM.
keywords:
  - pii
  - redaction
